        End Function

        ''' <summary>
        ''' Determines if this object and another object are equal.
        ''' </summary>
        ''' <param name="obj">The object to compare.</param>
        ''' <returns><b>true</b> if this instance and another object are equal; otherwise <b>false</b>.</returns>
